<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038507" n="165v"/>
<opener><del>Gratia </del>Accepi <date when="1718-11-19">heri</date> <rs key="B_1718-11-20_991170517051005501" type="letter">litteras</rs> Tuas gratissimas una cum <rs type="letter">epistola</rs>,
                    <lb/>quam <add>dicis</add> <rs key="place_GEO-3169070" type="place">Roma</rs> ad Te missam fuisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Monacho</rs> quodam<subst><del>, dicis</del><add>.</add></subst></opener>
<pb facs="1038508" n="166r"/>
<p><lb/>Rogo ut mihi significes nomen <subst><del>m</del><add>hu</add></subst>jus <rs type="person">monachi</rs>, et an Tibi idem sit
                    <lb/>notus, ut et an<del> ejus</del> <rs type="letter">epistola</rs>, quam ab eo accepisti, ab eadem
                    <lb/>manu fuerit exarata, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> qua fuit ea quam inclusam ad me
                    <lb/>misisti. Ego nullas unquam litteras <subst><del><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Monacho</del><add>ab illo</add></subst> accepi, neque
                    <lb/>ullus mihi <rs key="place_GEO-3169070" type="place">Rom<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="person">Monachus</rs> notus est. Suspicor aliquid myste<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rii hic subesse; antequam igitur ad eum scribas, rogo ut me
                    <lb/>de i<subst><del>ll</del><add>st</add></subst>a re certiorem facias, simulque mihi indices, an nullus
                    <lb/>Tibi <rs key="place_GEO-3169070" type="place">Rom<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> notus sit vir sincer<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fidei,<del> ad quem qui</del> per quem
                    <lb/>tuto ad <rs type="person">amicum</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3169070" type="place">Rom<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> degentem <rs type="letter">litteras</rs><!--ToDo--> mittere liceret. Quid
                    <lb/>Professores nostri sive boni sive mali de Te sentiant, ignoro. Quod
                    <lb/>vero attinet ad <rs type="person">y</rs>, ea de re coram agemus. Gaudeo Te acce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> doctrinis plenam; scire gestio, num
                    <lb/>quid Tibi de <rs type="organisation">Professione <rs key="place_GEO-2934691" type="place">Duisburgensi</rs></rs> significaverit. Nebu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lo quidam, qui sub nomine Caroli Baldi<!--persontag (Pseudomym) --> latere voluit,<note type="comment"><!-- ToDo: Pseudonym verifizieren. --></note> et quem 
                    <lb/>credo esse <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089923198" type="person">Verzagliam</rs>,<del>publica</del> typis edidit <rs type="biblio">libellum</rs> famosum,
                    <lb/>constantem duabus plagulis, plenum contumeliis et paralogis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mis, adversus observationes meas in <rs type="biblio">Theorema</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117498068">Fagnani</rs> publicatas
                    <lb/>in <abbr>Tom.</abbr> 29<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <abbr>art.</abbr> 5<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Diarii. Nescio an huic <rs type="person">nebuloni</rs> responsurus sim,
                    <lb/>stylus enim hujus <rs type="biblio">scripti</rs> plane non differt <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> stylo lib<subst><del>ri,</del><add>elli</add></subst> famo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>si, qu<subst><del>od</del><add>em</add></subst> contra <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>um</rs> edidit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzaglia</rs>, neque ovum ovo
                    <lb/>similius esse potest. Saltem in Tomo proximo <rs type="keyword">Diarii</rs> monebo, ejus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cemodi nebulones indignos esse quibus respondeatur.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute>
<lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1718-11-20">20. <abbr>9bris.</abbr> 1718.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
